@beautyofjoseon_official’s Red Bean Water Gel has been such a quiet skin-saver. It’s something I reach for when my skin feels out of balance, hydrated, but never heavy.

I remember loving their Dynasty Cream, but it was a bit too rich for my oily skin. This one, however, is made specifically for oily and combination skin, and you can really feel it in the texture, how it’s just cool, light, and calming. 🌬️

It’s formulated with 44% Haenam red bean extract for sebum control and as pore care, along with peptide complex that supports skin elasticity over time.

Meant for the days when I want my skin to feel soft, clear, and just quietly well cared for—the way your skin feels after a long day, washed and reset, when all it needs is something light, soothing, and simply nourishing. 🤍

I’ve been rotating through cleansing oils like a roulette lately, but one thing stays the same: cleansing oil is a non-negotiable in my routine, even with oily skin 👀 [AD]

@byjuccy’s Vinoberry Blended Cleansing Oil is made with over 40% sunflower seed oil, complemented by grape seed oil, grape juice extract, grape seed extract, and grape root extract—all known for their lightweight and antioxidant-rich properties. 🍇

I haven’t used a cleansing oil with grape seed oil before, so it was something new for me. It breaks down sunscreen and makeup well, emulsifies into a milky texture upon contact with water 🥛 and rinses off without any greasy residue. The scent is also sensorially therapeutic without being overpowering, something that I definitely enjoy during my night routine. 🌿

When you spend hours under bright studio lights, eye care becomes more of a necessity than a luxury. I’ve long incorporated @axisy_official’s Vegan Collagen Eye Serum into my routine, and it’s been a go-to, especially since I’m all about anything cooling ❄️. Primarily because of the cool-touch applicator. [AD]

The cooling texture is such a relief after long filming sessions 🎬, and it absorbs quickly without feeling heavy. While it doesn’t promise miracles, it does leave my under-eyes feeling refreshed and looking more awake 👀, even after all-nighters 🌙. It’s a simple, soothing step in my routine that helps keep my eyes looking bright and less fatigued 💚.

@laced_with_cherry x Raggedy Ann. Like a warm, nostalgic hug wrapped in color. 🍒✨

The Kawaii Picnic Palette is packed with vivid, playful shades and the dreamiest sparkly duochromes ✨ Sunny Day and Lots of Hugs have me completely smitten. The way they shift and twinkle in the light is just beautiful 🌈💖

The Soufflés in Black Cherry and Sweet Cherry have the softest, bouncy pudding texture that feels so fluffy to the touch, blending into a blurred, cloud-like matte finish ☁️🍒 And the Lit Gloss in Sweetheart adds that juicy, glassy shine to tie everything together 🍬💋 It’s sweet, dewy, and makes lips look extra plush.

I’ve done a few garden-themed setups, but this might be my favorite yet 🌿🌸 Still indoors, but I think I captured the cozy picnic charm 🧺 Maybe one day I’ll take it outside for real… but where? 😆

Tocobo’s Juicy Berry Plumping Lip Oil just launched SIX new shades to take your lips on a juicy, berry-filled adventure. Perfect for a fresh, natural shine and a smooth finish, this lip oil is all about hydration and gloss—without the sticky feel. Thanks to wild cherry extract, it’s like a berry smoothie for your lips. 😋💋🍇✨ [AD]

Ready for a juicy upgrade? 🌿 Whether you’re after a subtle plump or maximum volume, these shades have you covered! Shades #00 Frozen Berry and #11 Honey Lemon deliver maximum plumping, while the rest give a lovely, kissable boost of volume.

Here are the SIX new shades to choose from:
* #00 Frozen Berry: A sparkling icy blue ❄️💙 with a maximum plumping effect.
* #11 Honey Lemon: A zesty lemon yellow 🍋✨, packed with plumpness.
* #12 Cherry Ade: A refreshing icy cherry pink 🍒❄️ that gives your lips a glossy tint.
* #13 Choco Berry: A rich reddish chocolate brown 🍫🍓 with a smooth finish.
* #15 Coral Soda: A zesty, vibrant grapefruit coral 🍊🥤 with a pop of color.
* #17 Berry Milk: A cool, mysterious pale lilac 🍇🍼 that gives a natural touch of plumpness.
* #18 Cozy Pink: A muted pink 🌸 for that cozy, everyday lip look.

Get ready to plump up your pout and bring some serious shine to your smile! ✨

Snag yours now at @stylekorean_global and let your lips indulge in all that juicy goodness! 💕
